title: Mr Slash - Jewel Defense HD v2.1
description:
Do you like epic adventures full of action, strategy, gold, explosions, heroes and spells?
So, prepare yourself to play Mr. Slash and defend those who needs help.

Mr. Slash and the others heroes will fight against the evil to protect one small village that has been attacked by a witch who has the Dark Side as his ally.

The evil witch leads a group of ninjas, barbarians and witches. His plan... steal the seven magic stones and use their power to become the stronger evil source in the world.

What about online challenge? Mr. Slash now brings to you online leaderboard so you keep challenging people around the world to be best fighter.

Be brave and join us in this online quest around the world.

Features:

* EASY TO PLAY. Tested controls to all devices!

* THREE GAME MODES. We created three different game modes, each bringing your different obstacles and challenges.

* ENHANCED FOR YOUR DEVICE. Perfect game play! This game is definitely the most easy-to-play game for your device.
